div.div: The studious Yatora leaves a dry life of study and good manners behind for a new passion: painting. But untethering yourself from all your past expectations is dangerous as well as thrilling… (Source: Kodansha USA) Note: The anime received an early premiere on Netflix on Sep 25, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Oct 2, 2021.
The second season of Kimetsu no Yaiba. Notes: - This entry includes the TV version of Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugen Ressha-hen. - The eighth episode (5 December) airs with a runtime of ~1 hour.
